{"tid":756634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗喪屍版安祖蓮娜真面目曝光 外貌清純令人眼前一亮","createTime":"2018-07-26T07:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T07:13:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":89,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"c971a755e08223c3c09a24f48dda74f0ced32aee","tid":756634,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"伊朗德黑蘭女網紅塔瓦爾（Sahar Tabar），去年以一張知名影星安祖蓮娜祖莉為原型的喪屍照，一炮而紅。對於被傳曾整容動手術50次，塔瓦爾近日發布兩張照片澄清，指自己確實曾進行整容手術，但並非多達50次，喪屍照片全是靠特效化妝和修圖完成。<br />\n<br />\n自從喪屍照曝光後，有關塔瓦爾瘋狂整容和減肥的流言滿天飛，令她決定在Instagram上載整容前及整容後的照片釋疑。從照片可見，塔瓦爾的外貌非常清純，擁有一把秀髮及一對棕色大眼，令人眼前一亮。<br />\n<br />\n塔瓦爾承認自己曾抽脂，鼻子及嘴巴亦動過手術，但強調並非多達50次。雖然塔瓦爾分享的照片經常被指像「喪屍」，但她解釋，這些照片均是後製而成，「我都會以有趣的方式在臉上化妝，再用修圖軟件進行後製」，她認為這是一種藝術，亦是一種表達自己的方式。她又暗嘲相信她曾瘋狂整容的人如「活在18世紀」，連科技和化妝是甚麼都不知道。<br />\n<br />\n塔巴爾的照片引來網民討論，「整容前後一樣漂亮」、「整容前比較好看欸」、「這跟她之前的照片完全是不同人啊」、「只要微笑就很美了」、「原本的你真的很美」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180726/_2018072612115471156.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180726%2F_2018072612115471156.jpg&h=4e365a95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180726/_2018072612115311407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180726%2F_2018072612115311407.jpg&h=bc6c77b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/775624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F775624&d=MxhcFY12pvSLY75UTrpJRdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ef8412db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F775624&h=6fd880ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/775624</a><br />\n<br />\n差咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31e45bab801b2c5e62f366bc160ca9d1138bece","tid":756634,"uid":41634,"like":5,"dislike":65,"score":-60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"究竟受到咩刺激先會整到依家咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994be6a9c7abe3de96a9a7fa6f36f4dbfde0c90f","tid":756634,"uid":5190,"like":23,"dislike":6,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:57:29.000Z","msg":"「整容前後一樣漂亮」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d1545f6628bfe2acdaf5f3596014c532942c6a","tid":756634,"uid":18566,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"d31e45bab801b2c5e62f366bc160ca9d1138bece","tid":756634,"uid":41634,"like":5,"dislike":65,"score":-60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"究竟受到咩刺激先會整到依家咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"伊朗整容風氣都好盛行"},{"pid":"e59944360a6f5b9d8b5a8eabdf6682209b6ce96a","tid":756634,"uid":141869,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:08:03.000Z","msg":"做咩事整到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdce3d0379c2a9d58f7ba60d6a90ec8729cdd961","tid":756634,"uid":58335,"like":288,"dislike":0,"score":288,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"連登仔閲讀理解係咪全站部拎U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n。雖然塔瓦爾分享的照片經常被指像「喪屍」，<span style=\"color: red;\">但她解釋，這些照片均是後製而成，「我都會以有趣的方式在臉上化妝，再用修圖軟件進行後製」</span>，她認為這是一種藝術，亦是一種表達自己的方式。<span style=\"color: red;\">她又暗嘲相信她曾瘋狂整容的人如「活在18世紀」，連科技和化妝是甚麼都不知道。</span>"},{"pid":"f96bba86391ee6dcce98c1f0e6faadb1e36bca91","tid":756634,"uid":77092,"like":99,"dislike":2,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3e4896834a14d27fb53297b149078e32710761c","tid":756634,"